  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示 swaparoo 合约的部署和委员会初始化流程。核心角色是 Deployer、Zoe 合约框架、Committee 合约，还有一个投票者 Voter1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "V1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我把 Core 标注为 swaparoo<brdeployer，Ctee 标注为 swaparoo<brcommittee，V1 是 Voter1。部署流程是从 Core 发起 startInstance 调用到 Zoe 吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "startInstance"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Core 调用 Zoe 的 startInstance，传入 committee 参数。然后 Zoe 会启动 Committee 实例，committeeSize 设为 1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "committeeSize"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了：Core-)Zoe 调用 startInstance，Zoe--)Ctee 启动实例并传入 {committeeSize: 1}。接下来 Ctee 返回 creatorFacet 给 Zoe，Zoe 再返回给 Core。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "creatorFacet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来 Core 需要用 creatorFacet 去获取投票邀请。这里要注意，Core 是直接调用 Ctee 的 getVoterInvitations 方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "getVoterInvitations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，这里是 Core--)Ctee 的异步调用，标注为 E(creatorFacet).getVoterInvitations()，然后 Ctee 返回 invitationV1 给 Core，最后 Core 把邀请发给 Voter1？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "V1",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。整个流程就是：部署者通过 Zoe 启动委员会，拿到 creatorFacet，再获取投票邀请，最后分发给 Voter1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "V1",
        "creatorFacet",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成。我加上了自动编号，所有角色和消息流向都核对过了。Core 到 Zoe 是实线箭头，返回消息用虚线，最后 Core 到 V1 分发 invitationV1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "V1",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
